HTTP URL: 127.0.0.1:{{port_number}}/api/data/showtables

 This end point is GET request from the server, it will retrieve the data of number of tables and the full paths of the tables.

  For example:

   Input in ILegend Notebook:
   show_all_tables

   HTTP responses we receive:
    {
      "count": 2,
      "tables": [
        "mywarehouse::mydatabase::myschema::mytable",
        "warehouse1::db1::schema1::employee"
         ]
     }


  Output in ILegend Notebook:
  Number of tables: 2
  Tables:
  mywarehouse::mydatabase::myschema::mytable
  warehouse1::db1::schema1::employee
